data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home nestled on a spacious lot. As you step onto the property, you'll immediately notice the expansive outdoor space, perfect for enjoying the beauty of nature and hosting outdoor gatherings. The sunny foyer leads into the living room.  Natural light spills in through the large windows, enhancing the cheerful atmosphere that defines the entire residence. The generous-sized eat-in kitchen provides access to the patio and backyard. The master bedroom of this home boasts a spacious layout and a coveted walk-in closet. The master bedroom was created by combining two bedrooms and could easily be converted back into a 3 bedroom home. Adjacent to the master is a second generously sized bedroom. Step outside onto the large outdoor patio, an extension of the indoor living space. The expansive lot surrounding the home provides ample room for gardening, recreation, and enjoying the beauty of nature. Completing this home is a detached two-car garage and plenty of off-street parking. The home needs a little TLC.
